{
  "stem": "6277.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took him to a special block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called it [SPEAKING GERMAN] block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] block, it means a care, or a spare block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were people who weren't able to go to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I would take whatever I got, a piece of bread, a potato.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would take it to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one day I came, and he wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a big-- he was a strong man, and big.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he became so-- so slim and so weak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one day they would-- they would make selections.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They would come and pick up the people who are weak, taking to kill them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one day I came, and my uncle, my dear uncle, was gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to-- to look legal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They organized-- they want to-- all the evidence, what they had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the forest of Rumbula, the forest of [INAUDIBLE], they want to destroy the evidence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They want to burn the corpses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would take, they called it [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a special commando they would take every day, when we would stay-- they would take from the jail-- from the main jail in Riga, they would take people, they would take from the camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the morning when we would go to work, there was a German guard would come, and say to our elders, the [GERMAN], so-called, the elder of the column, what we would go-- the group, we would go to work.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would say, I need two people from our small group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he would take two people, whatever, you know, from the last ones, the middles ones, the first ones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he took two people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the people were taken to the place, to Rumbula.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
